      <li>METAPHORS AND ANALOGIES As you develop key messages and supporting points, decide on which rhetorical devices will make your narrative more engaging. Jobs uses metaphors in conversations and presentations. In one famous interview, Jobs said, â€œWhat a computer is to me is the most remarkable tool that we have ever come up with. Itâ€™s the equivalent of a bicycle for our minds.â€ Jobs likes to have fun with analogies, especially if they can be applied to Microsoft. During an interview with the Wall Street Journalâ€™s Walt Mossberg, Jobs pointed out that many people say iTunes is their favorite application for Windows. â€œItâ€™s like giving a glass of ice water to someone in hell!â€</li>
