  <li>
    <p>Jobs comes alive when he is up and moving onstage. He has seemingly boundless energy. When heâ€™s at his best, Jobs does three things anyone can, and should, do to enhance oneâ€™s speaking and presentation skills: he makes eye contact, maintains an open posture, and uses frequent hand gestures.</p>
